# Canonical-host redirects. Activates once www.duedatehq.com is bound to this
# Worker's custom domains (migration runbook). The apex (duedatehq.com) is the
# canonical host used for <link rel="canonical"> and the sitemap.
# http -> https is enforced by the Cloudflare zone "Always Use HTTPS" edge
# setting, not here.
https://www.duedatehq.com/* https://duedatehq.com/:splat 301
http://www.duedatehq.com/* https://duedatehq.com/:splat 301
